data.description: Welcome to a beautiful gem that is a must-see on the market! This 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers 1,974 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space, giving plenty of space for entertaining. When you enter this gorgeous home, you'll immediately become immersed in a feeling of comfort and sunlight thanks to its open floor layout. Whether you're lounging in the living area or preparing meals in the spacious kitchen, you'll find the layout promotes a warm, inclusive atmosphere that's perfect for both quiet nights in and lively gatherings.  The master bedroom is a haven unto itself, featuring a spacious walk-in closet. The private master bathroom adds an extra layer of convenience, making morning routines a breeze. The other three bedrooms are well-proportioned, offering flexibility in use as guest rooms, children's rooms, a home office, or whatever fits your lifestyle.  Step into the large, unfinished basement that awaits your creative touch. It's a blank canvas, ready for a luxurious home theater, a children's playroom, a home gym, or additional living quarters, the possibilities are endless!  Stepping outside, you'll be met with a large, vinyl-fenced backyard. This personal oasis is perfect for summer barbecues, winter snowball fights, or just a secure space for your furry friends to roam. Add to that a large, welcoming front porch where you can sip your morning coffee or enjoy cozy evening chats with loved ones.  The property also comes with a two-car garage, ensuring ample space for your vehicles or extra storage. Plus, with a smart security system, you'll have peace of mind knowing your home is always protected.  Located within the desirable Spring Grove School District, this property is not only an investment in a house but in a community renowned for educational excellence. The nearby amenities, all within a 15-minute drive, include parks such as Little Creek Park and Dunedin Park. These parks offer an array of outdoor activities for all ages.   Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, a growing family, or looking to downsize, this home has it all. Don't delay, come and see for yourself. Open houses on 4/6 from 11-1 pm and 4/7 from 1- 3 pm.
